WEBVTT

1
00:00:06.590 --> 00:00:10.427
<i>Our eyes remain on the Heavens.
and our resolve cannot waiver.</i>

2
00:00:11.136 --> 00:00:13.971
I promise you today that we will not rest

3
00:00:13.972 --> 00:00:17.935
until we find those responsible
for the theft of this asteroid.

4
00:00:18.852 --> 00:00:22.146
A resource that will bring
prosperity to our nation

5
00:00:22.147 --> 00:00:24.398
{\an8}and all nations of the world.

6
00:00:24.399 --> 00:00:28.153
{\an8}Earth comes first! Earth comes first!

7
00:00:32.323 --> 00:00:36.577
{\an8}President Gore let a handful of anarchists
and criminals run amok.

8
00:00:36.578 --> 00:00:39.956
{\an8}It's high time we bring Mars
back under control.

9
00:00:39.957 --> 00:00:42.333
{\an8}It's high time we put Al Gore
out of a job!

10
00:00:42.334 --> 00:00:43.918
{\an8}<i>…after an investigation found</i>

11
00:00:43.919 --> 00:00:47.255
<i>that its agents may have been involved
in the asteroid theft.</i>

12
00:00:47.256 --> 00:00:51.509
{\an8}<i>First man on Mars Lee Jung-Gil in a small
contingent of other North Korean ujunauts</i>

13
00:00:51.510 --> 00:00:54.054
{\an8}<i>have defected
from the People's Republic of Korea.</i>

14
00:00:57.683 --> 00:00:59.600
<i>On Wall Street. stocks continue to slide</i>

15
00:00:59.601 --> 00:01:02.103
<i>following reports
of the soaring national debt.</i>

16
00:01:02.104 --> 00:01:06.941
{\an8}<i>Samantha Massey was found guilty today
of conspiracy to violate the M-7 charter</i>

17
00:01:06.942 --> 00:01:09.986
{\an8}<i>for her part in the infamous hijacking
of the</i> Goldilocks <i>asteroid.</i>

18
00:01:09.987 --> 00:01:12.363
<i>Former astronaut.
Ed Baldwin. another conspirator.</i>

19
00:01:12.364 --> 00:01:16.367
<i>was tried in absentia unable to return
from Mars for health reasons.</i>

20
00:01:16.368 --> 00:01:19.620
<i>M-6 stations have finally shipped
the first load of iridium to Earth</i>

21
00:01:19.621 --> 00:01:21.290
<i>despite its tremendous worth…</i>

22
00:01:25.586 --> 00:01:28.921
{\an8}James Bragg clinched the presidency
by a landslide.

23
00:01:28.922 --> 00:01:32.592
<i>Al Gore is expected
to address the nation shortly.</i>

24
00:01:32.593 --> 00:01:33.926
Good evening.

25
00:01:33.927 --> 00:01:36.846
Just moments ago. I spoke with James Bragg

26
00:01:36.847 --> 00:01:41.058
and congratulated him on becoming
the 43rd president of the United States.

27
00:01:41.059 --> 00:01:42.810
If you ain't first. you're last.

28
00:01:42.811 --> 00:01:46.272
{\an8}<i>…cases of torture
by the CIA on Mars continue to…</i>

29
00:01:46.273 --> 00:01:48.941
{\an8}<i>Some alleged victims have been offered
clemency for their actions</i>

30
00:01:48.942 --> 00:01:51.319
<i>during the Happy Valley riot of 2003.</i>

31
00:01:51.320 --> 00:01:55.198
{\an8}I plan that my administration
will put Earth back in charge.

32
00:01:55.199 --> 00:01:59.494
{\an8}We simply cannot keep funneling money
to the moon. to Mars

33
00:02:00.037 --> 00:02:01.996
{\an8}without getting anything in return.

34
00:02:01.997 --> 00:02:04.207
{\an8}<i>…formed coalition known as ISN</i>

35
00:02:04.208 --> 00:02:06.918
{\an8}<i>vows to break the M-6 stranglehold
on iridium.</i>

36
00:02:06.919 --> 00:02:09.669
{\an8}<i>Members include China. Brazil. Pakistan…</i>

37
00:02:09.670 --> 00:02:11.172
<i>…vowed to clean up the agency</i>

38
00:02:11.173 --> 00:02:14.884
{\an8}following the exit of disgraced
NASA administrator. Eli Hobson.

39
00:02:14.885 --> 00:02:17.762
<i>Hurricane Katrina was downgraded
to a tropical depression</i>

40
00:02:17.763 --> 00:02:20.849
<i>in what has been one of
the mildest hurricane seasons in…</i>

41
00:02:24.478 --> 00:02:26.812
<i>Happy Valley's installation
of state-of-the-art</i>

42
00:02:26.813 --> 00:02:29.815
<i>radiation shielding towers
that deflect solar radiation.</i>

43
00:02:29.816 --> 00:02:32.109
<i>Mars workers on long-term contracts have…</i>

44
00:02:32.110 --> 00:02:34.278
<i>Keeping with the growing
automation trend on Earth.</i>

45
00:02:34.279 --> 00:02:36.656
<i>Uhuru Robotics has launched
a consumer model…</i>

46
00:02:36.657 --> 00:02:39.700
{\an8}<i>Increase in the number
of undocumented refugees on Mars.</i>

47
00:02:39.701 --> 00:02:41.160
{\an8}<i>known as Craters.</i>

48
00:02:41.161 --> 00:02:43.162
{\an8}<i>because they make the journey
in pressurized cargo crates.</i>

49
00:02:43.163 --> 00:02:45.081
<i>President Bragg narrowly won re-election.</i>

50
00:02:45.082 --> 00:02:46.999
<i>Promising to continue his Earth First…</i>

51
00:02:47.000 --> 00:02:49.710
<i>Helios Aerospace and others
are on the hunt for life</i>

52
00:02:49.711 --> 00:02:53.589
<i>and the billions of dollars in
applications such a discovery would bring.</i>

53
00:02:53.590 --> 00:02:57.260
<i>…this massive new piece of infrastructure
called a "space elevator"</i>

54
00:02:57.261 --> 00:03:01.222
{\an8}<i>will more quickly transport iridium
between the asteroid and Mars.</i>

55
00:03:01.223 --> 00:03:03.432
Actually. it's just basic chemistry.

56
00:03:03.433 --> 00:03:07.478
{\an8}<i>M-6 nations have confirmed the appointment
of Mars' next governor</i>

57
00:03:07.479 --> 00:03:11.274
{\an8}<i>Leonid Polivanov. A political protégé
of Soviet President Korzhenko has been…</i>

58
00:03:11.275 --> 00:03:14.068
{\an8}<i>President Ted Kennedy has died at 77.</i>

59
00:03:14.069 --> 00:03:16.571
<i>Many expect his nephew.
John F. Kennedy Jr..</i>

60
00:03:16.572 --> 00:03:20.157
<i>to follow in his footsteps
and run for president in 2012.</i>

61
00:03:20.158 --> 00:03:23.035
<i>…a flash mob. and it's the latest trend
sweeping the nations.</i>

62
00:03:23.036 --> 00:03:27.290
{\an8}<i>…2010 Winter Games
in protest of the M-6's…</i>

63
00:03:27.291 --> 00:03:30.001
{\an8}<i>…have begun amassing troops
along their border</i>

64
00:03:30.002 --> 00:03:31.335
{\an8}<i>in a dispute over iridium access.</i>

65
00:03:31.336 --> 00:03:33.671
{\an8}<i>I know it seems like
things are out of control.</i>

66
00:03:33.672 --> 00:03:35.882
<i>Watching your paychecks go lower</i>

67
00:03:35.883 --> 00:03:40.136
<i>while more of your tax dollars
get sent up to the Red Planet.</i>

68
00:03:40.137 --> 00:03:43.890
<i>The people up there.
they have no respect for the law</i>

69
00:03:43.891 --> 00:03:46.058
<i>or a hard day's work.</i>

70
00:03:46.059 --> 00:03:49.312
<i>But we will not back down.</i>

71
00:03:49.313 --> 00:03:53.816
Everything that makes the M-6
the greatest alliance on Earth

72
00:03:53.817 --> 00:03:57.028
only comes through decisive action.

73
00:03:57.029 --> 00:04:01.157
<i>And we will continue to
stand up for what is right.</i>

74
00:04:01.158 --> 00:04:06.955
<i>To stand up for our people.
Our planet. And for our way of life.</i>

75
00:04:08.582 --> 00:04:10.333
<i>Curfew is now in effect.</i>

76
00:04:10.334 --> 00:04:13.294
- <i>Authorized personnel only after 0100.</i>
- All right.

77
00:04:13.295 --> 00:04:14.713
<i>Thank you for your compliance.</i>

78
00:04:15.923 --> 00:04:19.509
<i>Curfew is now in effect.
Authorized personnel only after 0100.</i>

79
00:04:19.510 --> 00:04:23.221
Yeah. I was the same at that age.
Problems with authority.

80
00:04:23.222 --> 00:04:24.305
Fitting in?

81
00:04:24.306 --> 00:04:27.225
Right. But my mom
made sure it didn't go on my record.

82
00:04:27.226 --> 00:04:29.894
I couldn't have passed
hopper flight training otherwise.

83
00:04:29.895 --> 00:04:32.314
Well. remind me never to fly
with you at the stick.

84
00:04:32.940 --> 00:04:36.401
Don't worry. I barely get
one goddamn flight a week as is.

85
00:04:36.985 --> 00:04:41.405
<i>Unit 37. possible unapproved transit
in hallway Alpha 459.</i>

86
00:04:41.406 --> 00:04:43.450
Copy. dispatch. We'll take a look.

87
00:04:49.081 --> 00:04:50.958
Hey. I need to see your curfew pass.

88
00:04:53.043 --> 00:04:54.044
Stop!

89
00:04:54.837 --> 00:04:56.462
Oh. God.

90
00:04:56.463 --> 00:04:57.464
Look!

91
00:04:59.007 --> 00:05:02.886
Dispatch. 37.
We got another 10-17B. In pursuit.

92
00:05:03.971 --> 00:05:05.430
<i>Copy that. unit 37.</i>

93
00:05:13.522 --> 00:05:14.731
Goddamn it.

94
00:05:22.489 --> 00:05:23.532
Shit.

95
00:05:25.951 --> 00:05:29.371
Dispatch. unit 37. We lost 'em.

